  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Soak your <strong>skewers </strong>in <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> sweet potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into large, bite-sized pieces and add to a <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 25 min or until starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2136Step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
