    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely grate your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated ginger</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>mirin</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>honey</strong> (save the rest for later!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>yakitori sauce</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim, then cut <strong>half</strong> your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces and slice the rest finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2136Step-2-x200.jpg",
