            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> mayo</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a small splash of your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> in a small bowl – this is your<strong> Japanese-style mayo</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon and discard</p><p>Slice the<strong> cucumber halves</strong> finely into half moons and add them to a separate bowl with the <strong>remaining rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2136Step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
